  EPiSODE iNFO 
                                                        
                                                                        
  The recruits are halfway through the course, but three of them have   
  already dropped out, and the medics are barely keeping the rest on    
  their feet. Bear does his utmost to keep spirits up, but a shock      
  departure deals a blow to the group's morale. However, just when the  
  volunteers seem unable to take any more punishment, their training    
  enters a new phase that sheds light on another side of life as a      
  Foreign Legionnaire.
